The General Overseer of the Redeemed Christian Church of God (RCCG), Pastor Enoch Adeboye on Monday sent a message to the public saying that those who “dwell in the secret place of the Most High” will not be victims of the coronavirus pandemic affecting countries around the world. Quoting a passage from the bible, Pastor Adeboye tweeted a message accompanying the video. In the message, he said, “I want to assure you that so far you are in the secret place of the Most High, no virus can come near your dwelling. “Remember, being able to abide under His shadow involves you living a life of cleanliness: the basic things like washing your hands, keeping your environment clean…” Pastor Adeboye’s video tweeted using the handle, @PastorEAAdeboye follows: I want to assure you that so far you are in the secret place of the most high, no Virus can come near your dwelling. Remember being able to abide under his shadow involves you living a life of cleanliness. the basic things like washing your hands, keeping your environment clean.. pic.twitter.com/HQhnGQOHKx — PastorEAAdeboye (@PastorEAAdeboye) March 16, 2020  SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!!